<span id="an_16_12">12</span>. See Aptowitzer, "Issur Shetiat Mayim
B’sh‘at HaTekufah," *HaẒofeh*, II (1912), 122-6 and Ginzberg, "Arba‘
Tekufot," ibid., III (,913), 184-6, for a survey of the Jewish material;
*Teshubot HaGeonim* (ed. Musafia) §14; Joel, II, 24-5; *HaManhig*, *Hil.
Seudah*, §18; cf. Wuttke, 63 f., 78 f., 301, also 85: "Am Georgi-Tage,
